    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在乌克兰关于战争的谈判中将俄罗斯制裁放在桌面上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/bessent-says-us-could-adjust-russia-sanctions-for-ukraine-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表明，随着唐纳德·特朗普总统急于结束三年冲突的协议，对俄罗斯的制裁救济可能会在乌克兰的战争中进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/bessent-says-us-could-adjust-russia-sanctions-for-ukraine-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Feb 2025 13:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与乌克兰的批评抨击东欧集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/trump-slams-brakes-on-east-european-rally-with-ukraine-outburst</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普总统对乌克兰政府的袭击揭开对平稳的和平进程的押注，东欧资产的集会即将停止。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-20/trump-slams-brakes-on-east-european-rally-with-ukraine-outburst</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Feb 2025 11:18:12 GMT</pubDate>
